list. Remember, Oz from the hospital?

40:04.640 --> 40:05.709
Pen!

40:07.760 --> 40:10.513
This ain't even my CD.
-No, I know. It's mine.

40:10.600 --> 40:11.999
Hey, man. Good to see you.

40:12.560 --> 40:13.675
Hey, man!
