40:13.760 --> 40:16.797
Ooh! Hot girls. Y'all come on with me.
Y'all come over there.

40:19.040 --> 40:22.396
Thunda! I didn't want you
to sign. It's my demo!

40:23.760 --> 40:26.274
Okay, hi. And you
have a good night.

